  "page": "Jonos Arryn's rebellion",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #1e90ff;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Mbox notice.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/40px-Mbox_notice.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/60px-Mbox_notice.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/80px-Mbox_notice.png 2x\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Note:</b> The title of this article is conjecture and may be subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Jonos Arryn's rebellion</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/37_AC\" title=\"37 AC\">37&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\nThe <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\nIron Throne victory<br /><a href=\"/index.php/Hubert_Arryn\" title=\"Hubert Arryn\">Hubert Arryn</a> elevated to <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Eyrie\" title=\"Lord of the Eyrie\">Lord of the Eyrie</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Warden_of_the_East\" title=\"Warden of the East\">Warden of the East</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Targaryen.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/30px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/45px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/60px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a>/<a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a></b>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Arryn.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Arryn.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/20px-House_Arryn.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/30px-House_Arryn.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/40px-House_Arryn.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale of Arryn</a>, led by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">House Arryn</a>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Royce\" title=\"House Royce\">House Royce</a></li>\n<li>40 Vale <a href=\"/index.php/Bannermen\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bannermen\">bannermen</a></li></ul></li></ul></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Arryn.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Arryn.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/30px-House_Arryn.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/45px-House_Arryn.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/60px-House_Arryn.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/King_of_Mountain_and_Vale\" title=\"King of Mountain and Vale\">King of Mountain and Vale</a></b>\n<ul><li>Jonos Arryn's garrison</li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Targaryen.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/30px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/45px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/60px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> King <a href=\"/index.php/Aenys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aenys I Targaryen\">Aenys I Targaryen</a>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Targaryen.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/20px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/30px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/40px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor Targaryen\">Maegor Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Royce.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Royce.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cf/House_Royce.svg/20px-House_Royce.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cf/House_Royce.svg/30px-House_Royce.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cf/House_Royce.svg/40px-House_Royce.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Allard_Royce\" title=\"Allard Royce\">Allard Royce</a></li></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Arryn.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Arryn.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/30px-House_Arryn.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/45px-House_Arryn.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/60px-House_Arryn.svg.png 2x\" /></a> King <a href=\"/index.php/Jonos_Arryn\" title=\"Jonos Arryn\">Jonos Arryn</a>†</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Balerion\" title=\"Balerion\">Balerion</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Eyrie garrison</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Ronnel_Arryn_(king)\" title=\"Ronnel Arryn (king)\">Ronnel Arryn</a>†</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      King <a href=\"/index.php/Jonos_Arryn\" title=\"Jonos Arryn\">Jonos Arryn</a>†<br />Eyrie garrison†</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Jonos Arryn's rebellion</b> was a revolt by <a href=\"/index.php/Jonos_Arryn\" title=\"Jonos Arryn\">Jonos Arryn</a> against the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/37_AC\" title=\"37 AC\">37&#160;AC</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Background\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Background</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Rebellion\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Rebellion</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Aftermath\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Aftermath</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Background\">Background</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jonos_Arryn%27s_rebellion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Background\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale of Arryn</a> submitted to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a> during <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a>, thus losing their title of <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_Mountain_and_Vale\" title=\"King of Mountain and Vale\">King of Mountain and Vale</a>. The Targaryens allowed the boy king <a href=\"/index.php/Ronnel_Arryn_(king)\" title=\"Ronnel Arryn (king)\">Ronnel Arryn</a> to remain the ruler of the region henceforth as <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Eyrie\" title=\"Lord of the Eyrie\">Lord of the Eyrie</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Warden_of_the_East\" title=\"Warden of the East\">Warden of the East</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Rebellion\">Rebellion</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jonos_Arryn%27s_rebellion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Rebellion\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Upon the death of <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon the Conqueror</a>, people all over <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a> sensed weakness in the new king, <a href=\"/index.php/Aenys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aenys I Targaryen\">Aenys I Targaryen</a>. The new king's reign was troubled by <a href=\"/index.php/Harren_the_Red%27s_rebellion\" title=\"Harren the Red&#39;s rebellion\">Harren the Red's rebellion</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lodos_the_Twice-Drowned%27s_revolt\" title=\"Lodos the Twice-Drowned&#39;s revolt\">Lodos the Twice-Drowned's revolt</a> in the Iron islands, and the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Dornish_War\" title=\"Second Dornish War\">Second Dornish War</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Amid the other tumult, Ronnel's younger brother, <a href=\"/index.php/Jonos_Arryn\" title=\"Jonos Arryn\">Jonos Arryn</a>, began a rebellion atop the <a href=\"/index.php/Giant%27s_Lance\" title=\"Giant&#39;s Lance\">Giant's Lance</a>. With the aid of the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a>'s garrison, Jonos deposed and imprisoned Ronnel in the <a href=\"/index.php/Sky_cells\" title=\"Sky cells\">sky cells</a> and declared himself King of Mountain and Vale. King Aenys's initial reaction was to send his <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Alyn_Stokeworth\" title=\"Alyn Stokeworth\">Alyn Stokeworth</a>, with a fleet and an army to end the rebellion in the Vale. Worried that <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> would be left undefended in Alyn's absence, however, Aenys halted the fleet before it set sail and instead sent Alyn with a smaller force to to deal with <a href=\"/index.php/Harren_the_Red\" title=\"Harren the Red\">Harren the Red</a>. Aenys wanted to call a <a href=\"/index.php/Great_council\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Great council\">great council</a> to deliberate on how to deal with the various rebellions.\n</p><p>Acting without Aenys's countenance, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Allard_Royce\" title=\"Allard Royce\">Allard Royce</a> and twoscore <a href=\"/index.php/Bannermen\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bannermen\">bannermen</a> loyal to Lord Arryn began to lay siege to the Eyrie and demanded that Jonos released Ronnel from his cell. In response, Jonos flung his brother to his death through the <a href=\"/index.php/Moon_Door\" title=\"Moon Door\">Moon Door</a>, earning himself the nickname of Jonos the Kinslayer.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The situation remained a stalemate until the arrival of Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor Targaryen</a>, Aenys's younger brother, atop <a href=\"/index.php/Balerion\" title=\"Balerion\">Balerion</a>. At the sight of the fearsome <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragon</a>, the garrison betrayed Jonos, sent him to Allard through the Moon Door, and surrendered the castle. Maegor was not merciful towards the repentant garrison and ordered they all be hanged.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Aftermath\">Aftermath</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jonos_Arryn%27s_rebellion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Aftermath\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Hubert_Arryn\" title=\"Hubert Arryn\">Hubert Arryn</a>, a cousin of Ronnel and Jonos, was installed as the new Lord of the Eyrie and Warden of the East. Lord Allard approved of this choice as Hubert had married a <a href=\"/index.php/House_Royce\" title=\"House Royce\">Royce of Runestone</a> and had already six sons by her. For his efforts to put down the rebellion, Lord Royce was rewarded with <a href=\"/index.php/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">gold</a>, titles, and honors by King Aenys.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jonos_Arryn%27s_rebellion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Aegon's Conquest.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\">2.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Sons of the Dragon.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocol